---
import ServicePage from "../layouts/ServicePage.astro";
import { REFERRAL_DISCLOSURE } from "../data/site";
---

<ServicePage
  title="Referral Disclosure | Upper Cumberland Well Pump"
  description="Full disclosure of how Upper Cumberland Well Pump operates as an independent referral service, what it does not perform, and what visitors should confirm with providers directly."
  path="/referral-disclosure/"
  h1="Referral Disclosure"
  crumbs={[
    { name: "Home", path: "/" },
    { name: "Referral Disclosure", path: "/referral-disclosure/" },
  ]}
  isService={false}
  defaultService=""
  relatedLinks={[
    { label: "How Referrals Work", href: "/how-referrals-work/" },
    { label: "About This Service", href: "/about-this-service/" },
    { label: "Terms of Use", href: "/terms/" },
    { label: "Privacy Policy", href: "/privacy-policy/" },
  ]}
>
  <div class="disclosure-box">
    <p style="margin:0;"><strong>{REFERRAL_DISCLOSURE}</strong></p>
  </div>

  <h2>The Relationship, Spelled Out</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>
      Upper Cumberland Well Pump is an independent referral and lead-generation resource. It is not
      a contractor, a drilling company, a plumbing service or a water utility.
    </li>
    <li>
      It does not employ technicians, own service vehicles or drilling rigs, or maintain a physical
      office in the region.
    </li>
    <li>
      Requests submitted through the website may be shared, with your consent, with independent
      local providers for the purpose of responding to your inquiry.
    </li>
    <li>
      The website may receive compensation from providers in connection with referred requests.
    </li>
    <li>
      The service agreement for any actual work is between you and the provider. Upper Cumberland
      Well Pump is not a party to it.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>What Is Not Guaranteed</h2>
  <p>
    Submitting a request does not guarantee provider availability, contact, response time, pricing,
    licensing status, insurance coverage or acceptance of the job. Statements on this website about
    services, symptoms and processes are general information — not a diagnosis, quote or commitment
    on any provider's behalf.
  </p>

  <h2>What You Should Confirm Directly With Any Provider</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>
      The licensed individual's name, license number and current status for the applicable Tennessee
      license category (see <a href="/licensing-information/">licensing information</a>).
    </li>
    <li>Insurance coverage.</li>
    <li>Pricing, scope, schedule and any warranty — in writing.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Questions</h2>
  <p>
    Questions about this disclosure can be sent through the <a href="/contact/">contact page</a>.
  </p>
</ServicePage>
